    # Q.1: How many rows can Faye make with 19 pencils in each row?
    pencils_per_row = 19
    total_rows = 31 // pencils_per_row
    
    # Q.2: How many pencils are in each row?
    pencils_in_last_row = 31 % pencils_per_row
    
    
    # Q.3: What is the total number of pencils in all the rows?
    total_pencils = total_rows * pencils_per_row + pencils_in_last_row
    return total_pencils
